summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical overhead and underground distribution easements over portions of the southeast quarter of Section 1, Township 26 North, Range 3 East; Brighton Beach; vacated South 140th Street; vacated 24th Avenue South; vacated 40th Avenue South; the northwest quarter of Section 34, Township 26 North, Range 4 East; and Stimson Park Division No. 2, as described below and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
